                        "All our ingredients are sourced from local organic farms to ensure the freshest and healthiest meals for our customers. We believe in supporting our community while serving you the best!"
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <h3>Follow Us for Daily Updates! üì±</h3>
                <a href="#" class="social-icon">üìò</a>
                <a href="#" class="social-icon">üì∑</a>
                <a href="#" class="social-icon">üê¶</a>
                <a href="#" class="social-icon">üîó</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 {{restaurantName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>üìç 123 Food Street, Healthy City, HC 12345 | üìû +91 9876543210</p>
            
            <div class="unsubscribe">
                <p>You're receiving this newsletter because you subscribed to our updates.</p>
                <p>
                    <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a> | 
                    <a href="{{websiteUrl}}/preferences">Update Preferences</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
